  .screen#about
    .cell
      h2 About Datt
      p Datt is a community where people view great content and pay the creators, and people post great content and get paid for their creations.
      p The business model of Datt is to take a portion of payments between users rather than displaying advertisements, which better aligns the incentives of the company with the interests of the users.
      p Our goal is to empower users to find the best content, to properly own their content, and to get paid for the value they produce.
  
