  .screen#faq
    .cell
      h2 Frequently Asked Questions
      .question
        span Why is Datt better than reddit, Twitter, or Facebook?
        .answer
          p Datt has better content, you get paid for the work that you do, and you don't have to view targeted advertisements or give up your privacy.
      .question 
        span How do I get paid?
        .answer
          p Users pay each other bitcoin for creating content. The company and users take a portion of payments for work such as hosting or moderating content.
      .question
        span Why is Datt Decentralized?
        .answer
          p Users should own their content and shouldn't have to view advertisements or sell their privacy to use an app. By building on a decentralized protocol, our technology is aligned with our values.
      .question
        span Do I need to install anything?
        .answer
          p No, Datt runs in a web browser and can be used as easily as any web app. This is possible thanks to modern web technologies such as Web RTC, IndexedDB, and web workers.
      p Find out more detailed information in the 
        a(href="https://github.com/dattnetwork/dattdocs" target='_blank') Datt Documentation
    
